    {
      "chinese": "所謂燒墾，是老人家過去為了生活的智慧。首先尋找荒蕪或是山坡之地，雜草叢生，可以砍伐草木。經燒墾的荒地，可以種植農作物，這就是燒墾法。",
      "ab": "O misarafar hananay, o tadafenek no mato’asay to saki’orip itiya ho konini. Saka i’ayaw no pisarafar mikilim ho to masemotay caayay to kasikol ato masa’apilisay a pala, manga’ayay a fariwen, mipamatang, mipaloma to losay, oni koya misarafaray hananay no ’Amis/Pangcah.",
