    {
      "chinese": "燒墾的步驟，首先老人會鑽入樹林砍掉樹枝，一面用鋤頭挖地及砍伐草木。砍下大樹幹，可作日後柴火用的木材。完成後才開始砍伐、挖樹根或蘆葦。樹枝扛回家當薪柴。",
      "ab": "O tayal no misarafaray hananay, i’ayaw miletek to tapangan no kilang, mitistis to ca’ang no kilang malokasoy to, maherek to ta misatapang a mifariw to semot, mikarkar a mipitaw to lamit no kilang ato no talod, o ca’ang no kilang ’orongen a panokay malokasoy to.",
      "order": "2",
      "sound": "https://dzywvpqnys6mw.cloudfront.net/files/2021/12/07/14ee22eaba297944c96afdbe5b16c65b.wav",
